<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>麦肯锡见解与出版物</title><link>https://www.mckinsey.com/</link><description>麦肯锡见解与出版物 RSS 源</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 01 Sep 2015 08:44:43 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>将消费者和零售公司转变为软件驱动的创新者</title><link>https://www.mckinsey.com/industries/technology-media-and-telecommunications/our-insights/turning-consumer-and-retail-companies-into-software-driven-innovators</link><description>随着客户越来越期望无缝、引人入胜的数字体验，面向消费者的组织可以遵循六项原则，以像最成功的科技公司一样运作。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Sep 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.mckinsey.com/industries/technology-media-and-telecommunications/our-insights/turning-consumer-and-retail-companies-into-software-driven-innovators</guid></item><item><title>欧洲机械公司：通过创新实现平衡</title><link>https://www.mckinsey.com/industries/industrials-and-electronics/our-insights/european-machinery-companies-achieving-balance-through-innovation</link><description>在劳动力短缺加剧、通货膨胀和成本上升的情况下，什么可以帮助欧洲国家扭转局面？投资新技术、人才和产品；程序化并购和脱碳。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Sep 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.mckinsey.com/industries/industrials-and-electronics/our-insights/european-machinery-companies-achieving-balance-through-innovation</guid></item><item><title>与安·梅特勒 (Ann Mettler) 一起探讨资助清洁世界的前瞻性思考</title><link>https://www.mckinsey.com/mgi/forward-thinking/forward-thinking-on-funding-a-clean-world-with-ann-mettler</link><description>一位为欧洲能源转型提供资金的领导人谈到了必要的三个要素：速度、规模和简单性。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Sep 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.mckinsey.com/mgi/forward-thinking/forward-thinking-on-funding-a-clean-world-with-ann-mettler</guid></item><item><title>美国政府生产力：每位居民获得超过 2,000 美元的机会</title><link>https://www.mckinsey.com/industries/public-sector/our-insights/us-government-productivity-a-more-than-2000-per-resident-opportunity</link><description>政府仍然是提高生产力的最大机会之一。必须赋予组织改进的能力和动力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Sep 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.mckinsey.com/industries/public-sector/our-insights/us-government-productivity-a-more-than-2000-per-resident-opportunity</guid></item><item><title>麦肯锡填字游戏：拥抱“和”| 144号</title><link>https://www.mckinsey.com/featured-insights/the-mckinsey-crossword/september-5-2023</link><description>通过我们每周的填字游戏，以麦肯锡的方式提高您解决问题的能力。每个谜题都是以麦肯锡受众为中心而设计的，并包含一个微妙（有时不那么微妙）的商业主题供您发现。如果你想快速获胜，方向正确的答案可能不会成功。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Sep 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.mckinsey.com/featured-insights/the-mckinsey-crossword/september-5-2023</guid></item><item><title>填补空白：增加包装再生材料的供应</title><link>https://www.mckinsey.com/industries/paper-forest-products-and-packaging/our-insights/filling-the-gap-boosting-supply-of-recycled-materials-for-packaging</link><description>对包装中可回收成分的长期高需求可能会导致可回收包装材料的短缺。我们探索了三种提高 rPET 在美国市场供应的方法。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Sep 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.mckinsey.com/industries/paper-forest-products-and-packaging/our-insights/filling-the-gap-boosting-supply-of-recycled-materials-for-packaging</guid></item><item><title>随着市场重新开放，在英国能源零售业中取胜的策略</title><link>https://www.mckinsey.com/industries/electric-power-and-natural-gas/our-insights/strategies-to-win-in-uk-energy-retail-as-the-market-reopens</link><description>随着能源批发价格下跌，静态的英国能源零售市场开始发生变化。由于三分之一的客户希望更换供应商，以下是能源零售商可以满足客户需求的方法。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Sep 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.mckinsey.com/industries/electric-power-and-natural-gas/our-insights/strategies-to-win-in-uk-energy-retail-as-the-market-reopens</guid></item><item><title>G20必须推动可持续和包容性增长</title><link>https://www.mckinsey.com/mgi/overview/in-the-news/the-g20-must-press-ahead-with-sustainable-and-inclusive-growth</link><description>根据麦肯锡全球研究院的研究，全球约有 47 亿人（其中包括 G20 国家的 26 亿人）生活在经济“赋权线”以下。与此同时，印度和二十国集团其他成员面临着另一个紧迫任务：限制全球变暖。 Rajat Dhawan 和 Anu Madgavkar 在 Mint 杂志上写道，现在需要解决这两个问题。</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Sep 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.mckinsey.com/mgi/overview/in-the-news/the-g20-must-press-ahead-with-sustainable-and-inclusive-growth</guid></item><item><title>天然气在转向更清洁、更可靠的电力方面的作用</title><link>https://www.mckinsey.com/industries/electric-power-and-natural-gas/our-insights/the-role-of-natural-gas-in-the-move-to-cleaner-more-reliable-power</link><description>天然气可以通过为可再生能源提供备用能源供应，在美国电力供应脱碳方面发挥关键作用，但需要基础设施投资和市场机制。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Sep 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.mckinsey.com/industries/electric-power-and-natural-gas/our-insights/the-role-of-natural-gas-in-the-move-to-cleaner-more-reliable-power</guid></item><item><title>敏捷运营模式如何使风险和合规职能部门受益</title><link>https://www.mckinsey.com/capabilities/risk-and-resilience/our-insights/how-agile-operating-models-benefit-risk-and-compliance-functions</link><description>在将敏捷运营模式引入面向客户的一线业务部门后，金融机构也看到了敏捷对于风险和合规职能的好处。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Sep 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.mckinsey.com/capabilities/risk-and-resilience/our-insights/how-agile-operating-models-benefit-risk-and-compliance-functions</guid></item></channel></rss>